  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether there is a difference in muscle strength
      after anterior cruciate ligament comparing 2 surgery technics. Using either autograft
      hamstrings tendon or a autograft quadriceps tendon.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
